        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses specimens of <hi rend="italic">Utricularia</hi>.</p>  
<p>Mentions JR’s work on desmids [<hi rend="italic">The British Desmidieae</hi> [Desmidiae!?] (1848)].</p> 
